<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>: (الهَبَيَّخَة،<span class="c5"> كعَمَلَّسة:</span> الجارِيَةُ،<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>